locality: Flora of South Africa. Cape Province: Piketberg/Clanwilliam Division: Top of Piekenierskloof Pass (Grey's Pass), WSW. of Citrusdal.
Stawelklip (Piketberg). Dry Proteoid Fynbos (Campbell 1985); Vegetation cover 85%; Mature vegetation, at least 8 years old. Overstorey (Protea) c. 3 m; understorey c. 1 m.
Caledon Wild Flower Garden gentle S-SSE slope. Table Mountain Sandstone burnt 1983.
